About us

We are an amazing burger joint located locally in Huntington Beach, California. What makes us different from others is our unique twist on our delicous foods. For example, we love to go ham on toppings. Our hot dogs are stuffed to perfection and our burgers are monster! We also got the best shakes and sides. Come stop by our restaurant and tell us what you think!
